# .gitignore — Python project (tidy)
# Keep lock files (e.g. Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock) committed — do NOT ignore them.
# Adapt as needed for your tools and workflows.
# Reference: https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Python.gitignore

